These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, video-games, drawing, camping
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, salsa, techno
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, almond-milk, water
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, tram, trike
1. the person drinking coffee is the fan of techno##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's hobby is camping##2
3. the person drinking coffee is the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
6. the person driving the tram is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
8. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
9. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Hobby   | video-games | camping   | gardening  | drawing  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | techno    | metal      | salsa    |
| Beverage   | water | coffee | almond-milk | milk |
| Transport     | trike  | bus       | jet-ski    | tram     |

