.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, teacher, librarian, writer
House: modern, townhouse, ranch-style, palace
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, swimming, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the palace house is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the writer is between the ranch-style house and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the writer and the palace house##2
7. the modern house is on the far right##1
8. the teacher is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the librarian is on the right of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| Job   | police-officer      | teacher  | writer  | librarian |
| House           | palace      | ranch-style       | townhouse      | modern       |
| Sport         | lacrosse    | water-polo | swimming | ice-hockey |

