.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic, police-officer, teacher
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, martial-arts, scientific
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, cranberry, avocado, banana
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, quad-bike, bike, bus
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is the fisherman##1
 3. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 4. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the person eating cranberry##1
 6. the person eating banana is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is the police-officer##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the fisherman is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the mechanic is between the person eating asparagus and the teacher##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | fisherman  | teacher | mechanic     | police-officer |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action  | martial-arts | disaster       |
| Food           | cranberry       | banana    | avocado      | asparagus           |
| Transport         | boat | quad-bike   | bus   | bike         |

