.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, ferret, turtle, dog
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, baking, fishing, traveling
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, romance, scientific
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, ice-hockey, sailing, weightlifting
 1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is the owner of the ferret##1
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 6. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the owner of the turtle is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person watching romance movies is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Pet          | ferret         | turtle         | fish     | dog      |
| Hobby           | fishing | traveling | rock-climbing    | baking     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure      | romance       | scientific    | epic       |
| Sport         | basketball     | sailing       | weightlifting | ice-hockey |

