The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, jazz, punk
4 different games are played: poker, canasta, monopoly, billiard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, cycling, sailing
1. the fan of folk is between the person who's sport is sailing and the fan of jazz##2
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the fan of folk and the person playing billiard##2
3. the person playing monopoly is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person playing canasta##2
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
5. the person playing monopoly is the person playing monopoly##1
6. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
8. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
9. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Flower           | bellflower | balloon-flower | daisy  | orchid |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | punk       | folk     | jazz      |
| Game   | billiard   | canasta      | monopoly   | poker   |
| Sport         | cycling   | sailing    | climbing | cricket   |

